## Early game

**Hellas** on Mars (Extermination, Grineer Settlement, levels 8-10) is a quick
way to stock up early: Mars is one of Gallium's two signature planets, and its
enemies drop Gallium from the region resource pool, so a short Extermination
you clear repeatedly — with a Resource Drop Booster and Nekros Desecrate
re-rolling kills — adds up fast for a fresh account.

## Mid & late game

**Titania** on Uranus (Assassination, Tyl Regor, Steel Path) is the strongest
endgame option: Tyl Regor and the Grineer around him drop Gallium as enemy
loot on Uranus, Gallium's other signature planet, so repeat boss runs with a
Steel Path squad scale well per hour. Because it's an enemy drop, the Steel
Path passive, a Resource Drop Booster and a loot frame all stack to raise the
per-run yield.

